The project is composed by 2 main apps in turborepo:
- web: Our backend in payloadCMS
- app-expo: Our ios/android/web client

Web has this main technologies
- next-auth
- payloadcms
- lexical (the custom version)
- graphql

## App Expo
We need to develop it yet, It will be connected using graphql client using the schema that PayloadCMS exports using.

```shell
pnpm generate:graphql
# executes: cross-env NODE_OPTIONS=--no-deprecation payload generate:graphql
```


